import { FormControl, Input } from '@mui/material'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

const SectionBanner2 = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
        <Box component='form'>
            <FormControl>
            <Input />

        </FormControl>
        </Box>
        
    </Box>
  )
}

export default SectionBanner2
